    • Constructor Detail

      • Appointment

        public Appointment(java.lang.String date,
                   java.lang.String time,
                   int duration,
                   java.lang.String with,
                   java.lang.String where)
            throws java.time.format.DateTimeParseException,
                   java.security.InvalidParameterException
        Instantiates a new Appointment.
        Parameters:
        date - the date of the appointment matching APPOINTMENT_DATE_FORMAT
        time - the time of the appointment matching APPOINTMENT_TIME_FORMAT
        duration - the duration of the appointment in minutes
        with - a string where you can specify persons involved in the appointment
        where - a string where you can specify the place of the appointment
        Throws:
        java.time.format.DateTimeParseException - the date parameter doesn't match APPOINTMENT_DATE_FORMAT or the time parameter does't match APPOINTMENT_TIME_FORMAT
        java.security.InvalidParameterException - the duration is not a valid amount of minutes
